high_descs: heat and remove apple from microwave
Turn left and go toward the wall, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and take out the rightmost apple from inside.
Go to the microwave to the left of the fridge.
Open the microwave, put the apple inside and heat it up, then take it out.
Turn around and move forward, then turn right to go to the sink.
Put the apple in the left sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn to your left twice so that you are facing the fridge
Open the fridge, grab an apple from the shelf and close the fridge door
Walk to the left of the fridge to face the microwave
Put the apple in the microwave and cook it for a few seconds before taking it back out and closing the microwave
Put the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Grab an apple, cook it and put it in the sink
